  "detailed_description": "Crux: The Great Outdoors is a rock climbing game in which you move your climber’s hands and feet from hold to hold - but each hold will only let you hang on for so long.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209760/extras/02685c37926d157bde91b7cbb3b93ea0.poster.avif?t=1676620573\" width=568 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209760/extras/02685c37926d157bde91b7cbb3b93ea0.webm?t=1676620573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209760/extras/02685c37926d157bde91b7cbb3b93ea0.mp4?t=1676620573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Unique time-based puzzle mechanic:</i> Change your body position by moving hands or feet to a new hold - the hand hold determines how much time you have to move before falling off.<br><br><i>Plan ahead and execute: </i> You'll need to think ahead <strong>and</strong> execute flawlessly to beat all levels in the least amount of moves. <br><br><i>Enjoy the Great Outdoors:</i> Solve over 70 climbing challenges in nine peaceful and beautiful landscapes, from Caribbean coastline to rugged Highlands and red canyon walls.",
